    "For example, AI vendors were accountable for ensuring accurate AI models, and users to ensure proper intended use [51].",
    "In cases where the users were not the ones affected by AI output but the ones making decisions, users would be accountable for using the AI output responsibly and for communicating to the primary stakeholders about the AI output and how the AI output affected their decision making [37].",
